{"title": "Ride Proud, Rebel!", "description": "Drew Rennie, served as a cavalry scout in Confederate general John Hunt Morgan's command. He had left home in 1862 after a final break with his harsh grandfather, who despised him since his birth because of his mother's runaway marriage to a Texan. During the final year of conflict Drew has the additional responsibility of looking out for his headstrong fifteen-year-old cousin Boyd, who has run away from home to join Morgan's command and has a lot to learn in the school of hard knocks the army provides. The story follows the two of them and a new friend, Anson Kirby, through campaigns in Kentucky, Tennessee and later on deeper into the South, first with Morgan and later under Forrest. (Summary by Richard Kilmer)", "duration": 27311, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "358", "name": "Andre Norton"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/LibrivoxCdCoverArt33/Ride_Proud_Rebel_1312.jpg", "copyright_year": "1961", "genres": ["Action & Adventure Fiction", "Historical Fiction", "Action & Adventure"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "Richard Kilmer"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Richard Kilmer"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Barry Eads"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "Betty M."}], "sections": [{"section": 0, "title": "Preface", "readers": [4078], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/ride_proud_rebel_1312_librivox/rideproudrebel_00_norton_64kb.mp3", "duration": 159}, {"section": 1, "title": "Ride with Morgan", "readers": [4078], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/ride_proud_rebel_1312_librivox/rideproudrebel_01_norton_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1602}, {"section": 2, "title": "Guns in the Night", "readers": [4078], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/ride_proud_rebel_1312_librivox/rideproudrebel_02_norton_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1584}, {"section": 3, "title": "On the Run--", "readers": [4078], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/ride_proud_rebel_1312_librivox/ridepro